The paper deals with a multi-criteria decision-making problem, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of interval data fusion is a technique that can be applied in data science (cs.DS) and signal processing (cs.SI). The application of the method in supplier selection can also be relevant to computer engineering (cs.CE).
